{"tid":1135003,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱個friend話食Canteen，我屌到佢跪喺度","createTime":"2019-05-02T04:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T11:25:04.000Z","uid":150100,"like":70,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e63eb39acfece61dfd68d796df062e36e1faeba1","tid":1135003,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我地一班大學friend就成日出街食飯嘅，唔係自助餐就放題，唔係放題就食西餐据牛排燒羊架，平均一餐2、300蚊走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁講真，真係一啲都唔過份囉，話曬我地都係大學生，天之驕子嚟㗎嘛，唔通食啲100蚊都唔駛嘅垃圾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係偏偏我地其中一個friend就成撚日呻窮，今日佢竟然話不如食Canteen算啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：窮撚friend<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你老母，竟然叫我地成班大學生食豬餿，上次買咗個Canteen外賣返歸餵狗，連我屋企隻狗都唔撚食呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但係我冇錢&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇錢唔識問老母攞？你啞定弱智？<br />\n<br />\n屌屌下我實在忍唔撚住<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我跪喺度！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n條友又真係一嘢跪咗喺度，仲開始流埋馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我冇老豆老母㗎，屋企攞綜援㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：冇錢就咪學人埋堆啦，躪返屋企食狗屎啦<br />\n<br />\n之後我就同班friend由得佢跪喺度走咗去食好西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好波！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：樓主好嘢！"},{"pid":"6512c33cffedf2774365f429755f61d0a8118165","tid":1135003,"uid":202757,"like":60,"dislike":2,